data.description: Fall in love with the undeniable charm of this classic 4-sided Brick with wood Ranch sitting on 2.12 Acres! This home is ideal for the buyer that desires a country setting with quick access to I-20! This professionally renovated 3 bedroom /2 bath home with a bonus room (office or separate dining room) is very well maintained with much character, to be appreciated! Open the Front Door to an entry to the bright & open Living Area, with surround media speakers and new LVP throughout and all solid wooden doors throughout and also red oak shoe around all baseboards. The Laundry room is located just off the kitchen area and has an exterior door to the back porch. Come Enjoy the kitchen as it offers granite countertops, freshly painted cabinets, breakfast nook and the perfect amount of space for family gatherings and has all new white appliances. The Central Heat and Air does its job, but the ventless gas insert is definitely an added bonus! Enjoy having family & friends over to BBQ in the new back deck. You will easily be worry free, as the kids and pets play safely, outside, as the home offers a large front yard to roam and play. The driveway not only offers ease to drive in and out, with plenty of room for guest parking, in addition to a covered awning and a large, covered space to park your RV and wait that's not it. You have a separate storage shed with power. Come enjoy the beautiful flowers that bloom with calla lilies and gerber daisies and in the flower box is blue bells lillies and iris. At the mailbox are canna lilies and a fig tree in the front yard that produces a lot of figs every year. You've GOT to view this home TODAY and call this Home!
